song.title: ub1p ib2p
song.info: Made in Famitracker v0.2.9, NES 2A03-only. First played @ Pulsewave Feb. '09. Anyone who's acquainted with me well enough knows my love affair with cheesy overdriven squarewave guitar kwak inserted in cutesy moemoe material, ala Koike Masaya of UNDER17 and MOSAIC.WAV fame. See if you can identify all the cliches! Bonus! Here is the [url=http://www.nanjamonja.com/muzak/ub1pib2p.jpg]CD sampler cover pic for the song[/url]
